it.unibo.alchemist.model.implementations.strategies.speed

Class InteractWithOthers<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.alchemist.model.implementations.strategies.speed.InteractWithOthers<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpeedSelectionStrategy<T>, Serializable

    public class InteractWithOthers<T>
extends Object
implements SpeedSelectionStrategy<T>
    This strategy slows down nodes depending on how many "interacting" nodes are found in the surroundings. It is an attempt at modeling crowding slow-downs.

        inter - the molecule that identifies an interacting node
        speed - the normal speed of the node
        radius - the radius where to search for interacting nodes
